text: Þis is seo landscaru to trefwurabo.
Ærest æt pollcerr, ðenne be þære dic &lang weges.
Þon of þam wege on ða lytlan dic on easthealfe weges to pollhæscen adune be þam broce to rytcendeurion.
Þonne be ðam broce to carn nyþbran to deumæn coruan.
Þanon andlang weges to crucdrænoc, þanon to carrec wynn & eft ðanon to wollcerr.
Þis is se landscaru to trefualoc.
Ærest to þære dic þonne fram dice adune to ðam broce.
Of ðam broce to crouswrach &lang weges on ða dic.
Þanon to mainbiw to crucmur.
Þanon to carn wlicet &lang ðære to ðan broce.
Ðanon &lang stremes oð tnowpeter eft be dære ðic.
Þis is seo landscaru to crucwæþ.
Ærest æt nantbuorðtel &lang stremes oð lenbrun.
Þanon to cestelmerit, þanon west to wucowgenidor, west &lang dic oð broc.
Þanon to fonton morgeonec.
Þanon adune to broce ðær hit æt fruman wæs.
Þis is seo landscaru to trefdæwig.
Ærest æt penheal meglar suð to þam wege þanon to ðam forda on gerihte to erliwet.
Þanon forð &lang stremes to lyncenin.
Ðanon up to penhal meglar.
